item.title: Country's largest student housing block set for sale
item.author: THE SUNDAY TIMES
item.description:
DWS, a German asset management company, is mulling the sale of Ireland's largest off-campus student housing complex, writes Linda Daly.
The Sunday Times understands that the Deutsche Bank subsidiary will put Point Campus, a 966-bed complex, on the market in the coming weeks, after appointing Savill...
